{"arkId":"cl010099917","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099917","modified ":"2026-01-08","title":"Montre ronde","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ronde"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XIV (1643-1715) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1640 - 1660","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 1","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1640,"endYear":1660,"imprecision":"","text":"Milieu du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Weckherlin, Elias","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1688 - 1689","place":"Augsbourg","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 8320","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Fond du bo\u00eetier d\u00e9cor\u00e9 d\u0027une peinture \u00e9maill\u00e9e La Rencontre de Didon et En\u00e9e : accompagn\u00e9e de sa suivante, d\u0027un page et d\u0027un serviteur noir, la reine de Carthage s\u0027incline devant En\u00e9e, barbu, casqu\u00e9 et arm\u00e9, quittant son navire. Int\u00e9rieur peint d\u0027un paysage o\u00f9 coule une rivi\u00e8re et anim\u00e9 de deux chasseurs. Sur la carrure, six m\u00e9daillons ovales contenant des paysages vari\u00e9s s\u00e9par\u00e9s par des fleurons ocre jaune. Face ext\u00e9rieure du couvercle orn\u00e9e d\u0027une peinture copiant une oeuvre de S\u00e9bastien Bourdon, Les Adieux de Didon et En\u00e9e (conserv\u00e9e au mus\u00e9e des Beaux-Arts de Rouen) : suivie des m\u00eames personnages, Didon, visage \u00e9plor\u00e9e, appuie son bras sur la main de son amant s\u0027appr\u00eatant \u00e0 embarquer. Contre-\u00e9mail du couvercle peint d\u0027une sc\u00e8ne repr\u00e9sentant soit La Mort de Sapho ou Ariane. Cadran \u00e0 chiffres romains alternant avec des petits fleurons (demi-heures), le centre orn\u00e9 de rinceaux et de fleurs en \u00e9mail noir sur fond bleu. Mouvement dot\u00e9 d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 roue de rencontre ; coq \u00e0 un pied reperc\u00e9 et cisel\u00e9 de fleurs de fraisiers comme le cliquet. Piliers en forme de balustres.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Elias Weckherlin \/ Aug","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,8","displayDimension":"7,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"5,8","displayDimension":"5,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,8","displayDimension":"2,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nTechnique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Augsbourg = Ausgburg (Allemagne-\u003EBavi\u00e8re)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Jules-Ren\u00e9 Olivier (1855-1933), horloger-collectionneur ; legs de sa s\u0153ur Marie-Julie Olivier, n\u00b0 711, 1935.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme Olivier, Marie-Julie","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"Olivier, Jules-Ren\u00e9","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode"